  <brief_title>A Trial of Oral BEZ235 and BKM120 in Combination With Paclitaxel With or Without Trastuzumab</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Phase Ib Multi-center, Open-label, 4-arm Dose-escalation Study of Oral BEZ235 and BKM120 in Combination With Weekly Paclitaxel in Patients With Advanced Solid Tumors and Weekly Paclitaxel/Trastuzumab in Patients With HER2+ Metastatic Breast Cancer</official_title>
