  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of the trial is to determine the maximum tolerated dose (MTD) of BEZ235 and
      BKM120 in combination with weekly paclitaxel and weekly paclitaxel/trastuzumab.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
